    "direction": null,
    "content": "<p>Consider a simply supported beam PQ as shown in the figure. A truck having 100 kN on the front axle and 200 kN on the rear axle, moves from left to right. The spacing between the axles is 3 m. The maximum bending moment at point R is _________ kNm. (in integer)</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/fly/@width/image/jaoe38c1m1p6fxyb/86c17c1d-3792-4106-9c82-4ad4e83ad26f/695a2820-7f42-11ef-b740-5762ac8bb4a2/file-jaoe38c1m1p6fxyc.png?format=png\" data-orsrc=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/image/jaoe38c1m1p6fxyb/86c17c1d-3792-4106-9c82-4ad4e83ad26f/695a2820-7f42-11ef-b740-5762ac8bb4a2/file-jaoe38c1m1p6fxyc.png\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"max-width:100%;height:auto;display:block;margin:0 auto;max-height:40vh;vertical-align:baseline\" alt=\"GATE CE 2022 Set 1 Strength of Materials Or Solid Mechanics - Shear Force and Bending Moment Question 5 English\"></p>",
    "options": [],
    "correct_options": [],
    "answer": "180",
    "explanation": "<p><img src=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/fly/@width/image/jaoe38c1m1p6jcco/5a745358-a92a-4173-8ea5-709f58ad858c/c7e72c80-7f42-11ef-b740-5762ac8bb4a2/file-jaoe38c1m1p6jccp.png?format=png\" data-orsrc=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/image/jaoe38c1m1p6jcco/5a745358-a92a-4173-8ea5-709f58ad858c/c7e72c80-7f42-11ef-b740-5762ac8bb4a2/file-jaoe38c1m1p6jccp.png\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"max-width:100%;height:auto;display:block;margin:0 auto;max-height:40vh;vertical-align:baseline\" alt=\"GATE CE 2022 Set 1 Strength of Materials Or Solid Mechanics - Shear Force and Bending Moment Question 5 English Explanation\"></p>\n<p>$${{ab} \\over L} = {{1 \\times 4} \\over 5} = 0.8$$ m</p>\n<p>To get maximum BM at R</p>\n<p>$$B{M_{\\max }} = 200 \\times {{ab} \\over L} + 100 \\times y$$</p>\n<p>$${{ab/L} \\over b} = {y \\over {4 - 3}} \\Rightarrow {{0.8} \\over 4} = {y \\over 1} = 0.2$$ m</p>\n<p>$$B{M_{\\max }} = 200 \\times 0.8 + 100 \\times 0.1 = 180$$ kNm</p>",
    "topic": null,
    "year": 2022,
    "yearKey": "gate-ce-2022-set-1",
    "difficulty": null
  },
